11#ifndef RTC_BASE_TIME_TIMESTAMP_EXTRAPOLATOR_H_
12#define RTC_BASE_TIME_TIMESTAMP_EXTRAPOLATOR_H_
13
14#include <stdint.h>
15
16namespace webrtc {
17
18// Not thread safe.
19class TimestampExtrapolator {
20 public:
21 explicit TimestampExtrapolator(int64_t start_ms);
22 void Update(int64_t tMs, uint32_t ts90khz);
23 int64_t ExtrapolateLocalTime(uint32_t timestamp90khz);
24 void Reset(int64_t start_ms);
25
26 private:
27 void CheckForWrapArounds(uint32_t ts90khz);
28 bool DelayChangeDetection(double error);
29 double _w[2];
30 double _pP[2][2];
31 int64_t _startMs;
32 int64_t _prevMs;
33 uint32_t _firstTimestamp;
34 int32_t _wrapArounds;
35 int64_t _prevUnwrappedTimestamp;
36 int64_t _prevWrapTimestamp;
37 const double _lambda;
38 bool _firstAfterReset;
39 uint32_t _packetCount;
40 const uint32_t _startUpFilterDelayInPackets;
41
42 double _detectorAccumulatorPos;
43 double _detectorAccumulatorNeg;
44 const double _alarmThreshold;
45 const double _accDrift;
46 const double _accMaxError;
47 const double _pP11;
48};
49
50} // namespace webrtc
51
52#endif // RTC_BASE_TIME_TIMESTAMP_EXTRAPOLATOR_H_
